<div class="container_12 form">
	<%= erb :_backend_menu %>
	<div class="grid_12"><h2>Help:</h2></div>
	<div class="grid_9">
		<p id="introText">El Co is an easy to use app. Simply watch a video to learn how to use each section of the app.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="grid_12"><hr /></div>
	<div class="clear"></div>
	<div class="grid_6 prefix_3 suffix_3">
		<h2>How to add a movie:</h2>
		<p style="margin-bottom:20px;">This video will teach you how to add a movie to your movie data base. Movies are listed chronological order in which you added them. So, old movies at the top, new movies at the bottom. To delete a movie from the data base permenantly click the red "Remove Movie" link.</p>
		<iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/40889154" width="500" height="375" frameborder="0" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></iframe>
	</div>
	<div class="grid_12">
		<hr />
	</div>
	<div class="grid_6 prefix_3 suffix_3">
		<h2>How to add a movie to Now Showing:</h2>
		<p style="margin-bottom:20px;">This video will teach you how to add a movie from your database to the "Now Showing" slot. You can add as many movies as you like to this slot, however, the page is designed to show one now showing movie.</p>
		<iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/40889153" width="500" height="375" frameborder="0" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></iframe>
	</div>
	<div class="grid_12">
		<hr />
	</div>
	<div class="grid_6 prefix_3 suffix_3">
		<h2>How to add a movie to Upcoming:</h2>
		<p style="margin-bottom:20px;">This video will teach you how to add a movie from your database to the "Upcoming" section. The Upcoming section is designed to show no more than 3 movies at a time. If you do not add 3 movies it will appear unfinished. If you add more than 3 movies it will appear crowded.</p>
		<iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/40889040" width="500" height="375" frameborder="0" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></iframe>
	</div>
	<div class="clear"></div>
</div>